subject: Decisions and Verdicts
America's Cup
Sailboats and Sailing
lead_paragraph: The New York Supreme Court’s Appellate Division unanimously upheld a lower court’s order that the Swiss choice of Ras al-Khaimah, United Arab Emirates, did not qualify to host the America’s Cup.
